MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: (packages/game-cartridges/.+\.tsx?$|apps/client/src/cartridges/.+\.tsx?$)
MATCH_CONTENT: (theme\.colors\.|themeRef\.current.*colors\.|t\.colors\.|colors\[[^|]+\])
ADVISORY: |
  Valid `theme.colors` keys (from CartridgeTheme in
  packages/ui-kit/src/cartridge-theme.ts):

      gold, pink, danger, green, orange, info,
      bg, bgSubtle, panel, border, text, textDim

  DO NOT guess common CSS names — these DO NOT exist: surface, accent,
  primary, secondary, muted, foreground, background, warn, success.

  Typecheck will catch a wrong key but only after you rebuild. Grep or
  pick from this list the first time.

  If you want a role you don't see (e.g., "surface"), use `panel` or `bgSubtle`.
